ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: Text that describes the entity in more detail.

ivardefs.name: detail_
ivardefs.desc: Tagged value pairs for conveying additional information about the entity.

ivardefs.name: lifecycle
ivardefs.desc: Identifier for the data life-cycle stage for the entity.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A name of the entity in the audit event.

ivardefs.name: query
ivardefs.desc: The query parameters for a query-type entities.

ivardefs.name: role
ivardefs.desc: Code representing the role the entity played in the event being audited.

ivardefs.name: securityLabel_
ivardefs.desc: Security labels for the identified entity.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The type of the object that was involved in this audit event.

ivardefs.name: what
ivardefs.desc: Identifies a specific instance of the entity. The reference should be version specific.

properties.desc: Specific instances of data or objects that have been accessed.
